## Summary
This documentation explains Conversion Drivers in Amplitude's Funnel Analysis, a feature that automatically analyzes user events between funnel steps to identify behaviors most strongly correlated with conversion or drop-off. It provides metrics like correlation score, behavior frequency, user engagement percentage, and conversion time to help understand which actions drive important outcomes in the customer journey.

